plain text

<red>colored</red> and <blue>more</blue>

<bold><italic>nested</italic></bold>

Escapes: \<red>not a tag\</red> \\ \<\> \</\>

Custom tag: <custom_tag>text</custom_tag>

Attribute no quotes: <font:uniform>text</font>

Attribute with colon payload: <click:run_command:/say hello>click me</click>

Quoted attribute: <click:run_command:"/say hello world">click</click>

Tag that starts with lots of <: <<<<<<<<red>

Tag with extra whitespace: <red   >spacey</red>

Adjacent tags: <red>A</red><blue>B</blue><green>C</green>

Empty content: <red></red>

Self-like tag (if your grammar has it): <reset>

Newlines:
<red>line1
line2</red>

Literal angle brackets: 1 < 2 and 3 > 2

Mismatched nesting: <red><blue>X</red></blue>

Deep nesting stress:
<bold><italic><underlined><strikethrough>stress</strikethrough></underlined></italic></bold>

Gradient-ish:
<gradient:red:blue>Hello</gradient>

Hex color:
<#12abEF>hex</#12abEF>

Unicode / surrogate pairs:
Hello—世界—🙂—𝄞

Lots of text (performance):
aaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaa <red>bbbbbbbbbbbb</red> ccccccccccccccccccccccccccccccccccccccccccccccccccc